Package com.codisimus.plugins.phatloots.loot

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandLoot
    A CommandLoot is a Command which may be executed from the player or the console
    Experience
    An Experience is a range of experience to be given to the looter
    Gem
    A Gem is a SocketGem ItemStack generated by the plugin MythicDrops
    Item
    An Item is the Loot representation of an ItemStack
    Loot
    A Loot has a probability of looting
    LootBundle
    A LootBundle is a collection of items, commands, money, and experience that has been rolled for
    LootCollection
    A Collection is a list of Loots which has a unique name
    Message
    A Message is an in game message which is shown to the looter
    Money
    A Money is a range of money to be given to the looter
    MythicDropsItem
    A MythicDropsItem is an ItemStack generated by the plugin MythicDrops
    UnidentifiedItem
    An UnidentifiedItem is an ItemStack generated by the plugin MythicDrops
